        "condition_expr": "is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"TownSolitudeFaction\") or is_in_faction(actorUUID, \"GuardFactionHaafingar\")",
        "content": "Dead Men's Respite is the Nordic tomb of King Olaf One-Eye east of Dragon Bridge — the ghost of his rival Svaknir wanders inside, and the Verse of Olaf still rests where it was hidden.",
